<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-feel-honoured-to-do-sth">be / feel honoured to do sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>做某事感到荣幸：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was honoured to have been mentioned in his speech.
很荣幸他在讲话中提到了我。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I feel very honoured to have been able to take on this role.
能够担当这一角色，我感到非常荣幸。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 4</footer></div></div>